#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-specification/blob/main/specification/overview.md#resources[resource] is a representation\n"
"of the entity that is producing telemetry, it adds attributes to the exported trace or metric to characterize who is producing the telemetry. Quarkus follows the https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/#resources[resources auto-configuration] specified by the Java OpenTelemetry SDK."
msgstr "Um link:https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-specification/blob/main/specification/overview.md#resources[recurso] é uma representação da entidade que está gerando telemetria; ele adiciona atributos ao rastreamento ou à métrica exportada para caracterizar quem está gerando a telemetria. O Quarkus segue a link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/#resources[configuração automática de recursos] especificada pelo SDK do Java OpenTelemetry."

